room_title: Escape room "Temple Escape" by Shipwrecked in New York
room_description: Admit it, who hasn't wanted to explore temple ruins and find artifacts made of gold?  Now is your chance to be a true treasure hunter.  But BEWARE!!! With great wealth comes great consequences. Make the wrong move and you may be trapped forever.  Locate all the artifacts and solve the ancient puzzles to retrieve the golden skull and make your way to freedom, but do it quick, the 25-minute timer is ticking down fast!
